data.name: GMO Cookies
data.details: GMO provides a deep body high that feels like a classic indica, with the uplifting cerebral vibrancy of its Chemdawg parent. This strain can lock you to the couch, so plan accordingly—prep snacks, pour yourself a glass of water, and settle in for deep relaxation.
